      • exec

        public void exec(Dataset inputDataset,
                 Model initialModel,
                 List<Var> variables,
                 List<BindingHashMapOverwrite> values)
        Executes the GENERATE Clause. Uses the given inputDataset for the subsequent SPARQL GENERATE queries. Augments the given initialModel with the generated RDF triples. Use the given variables and values to generate triples. The behaviour if initialModel is one of the RDF graphs in inputDataset is not specified.
        Specified by:
        exec in interface GeneratePlan
        Parameters:
        inputDataset - the Dataset to use for the SPARQL SELECT part of the query.
        initialModel - the Model to augment with the generated RDF triples.
        variables - the set of bound variables.
        values - the set of bindings.
